{"data":{"recipes":{"title":"Kabanos and lentil casserole","preparationTime":15,"difficulty":"middle","totalTime":0,"ingredients":["1 medium onion"," peeled and sliced","4 Cloves of garlic"," peeled and crushed"," or to taste","1 bell pepper sliced"," seeds and centre removed.","6 kabanos sausages"," cut into slices","6 medium mushrooms"," brushed clean and sliced","4 tomatoes"," quartered","600 ml carton of lentil and bacon soup","&#189; teaspoon of Chile flakes (optional)","Olive oil","sea salt and freshly ground black pepper","Chopped parsley to garnish"],"instructions":"Gently saut√© the onions, peppers and garlic in oil that has been seasoned well with black pepper and chili flakes. This will take about 5 minutes. Place the onion mix in the base of a casserole dish, stir in the mushrooms add the kabanos sausages and cover with the lentil soup.,Arrange the tomatoes on the top.,Cover with foil and bake for 25 minutes,Remove the foil and bake for a further 15 minutes,Taste and season if needed","relationships":{"category":{"name":"Main course"},"image":{"relationships":{"imageFile":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3409090909090908,"src":"/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/b6442/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg","srcSet":"/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/d3fc2/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 118w,\n/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/17c91/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 235w,\n/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/b6442/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 470w,\n/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/a53d9/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 705w,\n/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/3ce55/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 940w,\n/static/25e31c7296d76154b07ba204a62a356d/704cb/egyptian_food_koshary.jpg 1200w","sizes":"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px"}}}}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/recipes/24/"}}